HEADWORD: Moneywort
<hw>Mon"ey*wort`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A trailing plant (<spn>Lysimachia Nummularia</spn>), with rounded
opposite leaves and solitary yellow flowers in their axils.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

